==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Indocile
<hw>In*doc"ile</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>indocilis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>indocile</ets>. See <er>In-</er> not,
and <er>Docile</er>.]</ety> <def>Not teachable; indisposed to be taught,
trained, or disciplined; not easily instructed or governed; dull;
intractable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Indocility</ent>⟦br⟧
